05:22.170 --> 05:24.604
- I want what's best for the city, sir.

05:26.975 --> 05:29.205
<i>- It is the court's view...</i>

05:29.344 --> 05:31.835
that the state has failed...
<font color="#D900D9">(EXCLAMATIONS OF DISGUST)</font>

05:31.980 --> 05:33.709
