- How come you see these looks
and I don't see these looks?

10:31.812 --> 10:34.332
- Because you only see the best in people.
It's your fatal flaw.

10:34.382 --> 10:35.474
- And what's yours?

10:36.284 --> 10:38.809
- Not being able to see the best in people.

10:38.953 --> 10:40.352
- Not even me?

10:40.488 --> 10:42.479
- You're the exception, you know that.

10:43.491 --> 10:45.152
