calling collect again, Katy, I swear.

11:52.193 --> 11:54.718
- It's called <i>collections,</i> Billy. Y'know,

11:54.862 --> 11:56.782
because you don't like
to charge nobody up front.

11:56.797 --> 11:59.163
- How's it comin'?
- Uh, you know that theory of yours

11:59.300 --> 12:01.234
