if somebody owes you?

12:01.369 --> 12:03.360
We're broke. Hee-hee.

12:03.804 --> 12:05.567
Yeah, no, I'm still holding.

12:06.574 --> 12:07.563
Yeah.

12:10.211 --> 12:11.576
- What is this?

12:11.712 --> 12:14.579
- Some guy from Staten Island
said he's gonna find you and kill you.

12:14.715 --> 12:17.081
- Call him back.
Tell him he owes me a camera.

12:17.218 --> 12:19.812
- Oh. Oh, he just stepped out?

12:21.021 --> 12:22.386
Oh, yeah, just now?

12:23.591 --> 12:28.153
Okay, well... you tell him he's got
till the close of business today

12:28.295 --> 12:30.820
to call Katy from Billy Taggart's office.

12:31.599 --> 12:34.500
