of the eight grand you owe me?

13:04.899 --> 13:07.459
Does that work for you?
<i>- How about I pay you in instalments?</i>

13:07.601 --> 13:10.601
- Yeah, three instalments of 2,650.
First payment this Friday. Talk to Katy.

13:10.638 --> 13:12.333
<i>Jimmy. Hey, buddy.</i>
It's Billy.

13:12.473 --> 13:15.306
<i>- What's up, Bill?</i>
- Oh, just checkin' on you.

13:15.443 --> 13:18.003
Hoping I can get that payment, buddy.
<i>- Aw, well, y'know,</i>

13:18.145 --> 13:20.204
<i>things have been a little slow here, y'know.</i>

13:20.347 --> 13:22.747
<i>I've been, uh...
really going through some rough times.</i>

13:22.883 --> 13:26.785
<font color="#808080">WOMAN:</font> <i>How many times did you catch him,
literally with his pants down,</i>

13:26.921 --> 13:31.722
