<i>- I'm supposed to foot the goddamn bill?!</i>

13:35.596 --> 13:37.757
<i>How many times, Billy? Tell me that!</i>

13:37.898 --> 13:40.958
- Eight times, Amber,
for a total billing of $4,000. C'mon!

13:41.101 --> 13:43.763
<i>- Send him the invoice, then!</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(DISCONNECTION)</font>

13:43.904 --> 13:46.839
<font color="#808080">MAN:</font> <i>Listen, Billy,
