13:46.974 --> 13:48.942
- I want my fuckin' money!

13:49.076 --> 13:51.374
<i>- Yeah, you'll get it. Neveruary.</i>

13:51.512 --> 13:53.036
- What kind of man are you, Dave?

13:53.180 --> 13:55.910
