the original question still remains.

01:23:09.599 --> 01:23:12.227
What would you have done
to reverse the debt?

01:23:13.470 --> 01:23:15.404
- Tha...
- Don't worry about it, Councilman!

01:23:15.538 --> 01:23:17.506
Nicky fixed it.
