01:23:17.641 --> 01:23:19.404
<font color="#D900D9">(CHEERING)</font>

01:23:29.653 --> 01:23:31.712
- Two honks for trouble. Got it.

01:23:31.855 --> 01:23:34.153
- Lean your seat back all the way, okay?
- Okay.

01:23:34.290 --> 01:23:35.655
- I'll be right back.

01:24:02.152 --> 01:24:03.551
You know who I am?
- No!

01:24:03.687 --> 01:24:06.087
- 'Cause I know who you are, Todd.
I know what you are,

01:24:06.222 --> 01:24:07.849
you piece of shit!
- What? Watch it! Ah!

01:24:07.991 --> 01:24:09.720
- You set up Andrews to die!
- No. No.

01:24:09.859 --> 01:24:11.579
- You set him up!
You arranged that meeting,

01:24:11.695 --> 01:24:13.526
and you lured him out!
- No, I didn't.

01:24:13.663 --> 01:24:16.393
- You let him walk into an ambush.
- No, I didn't kill him!

01:24:16.533 --> 01:24:19.366
- You want to fuckin' play games with me?!
Shut your fuckin' mouth!

01:24:19.502 --> 01:24:21.783
You're a fucking liar. You're a liar.
- I didn't kill him.

01:24:21.838 --> 01:24:24.204
- Ah... Ah... Ah, no.
- You wanna lie to me?

01:24:24.340 --> 01:24:26.103
<font color="#D900D9">(GUN COCKING)</font>
- I'm not lying.

01:24:26.242 --> 01:24:28.107
He was my friend.
- What?!

01:24:28.244 --> 01:24:30.371
- He was my friend!!
- Get up!

01:24:30.513 --> 01:24:31.707
Now!

01:24:33.183 --> 01:24:36.209
What are you saying?
Tell me what the fuck is going on!

01:24:36.352 --> 01:24:37.751
- Please stop hitting me!

01:24:37.887 --> 01:24:39.650
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font> I didn't know!

01:24:40.724 --> 01:24:42.919
I was just there to give him something!

01:24:43.059 --> 01:24:45.960
I-I was down on the corner
and I was waiting for him,

01:24:46.096 --> 01:24:47.927
and I saw him coming down the stairs

01:24:48.064 --> 01:24:49.588
and I waved, okay?

01:24:49.733 --> 01:24:53.169
I was gonna give him something
to help Valliant win!

01:24:53.303 --> 01:24:56.136
