that sonofabitch Hostetler!

01:24:56.272 --> 01:24:59.070
- That doesn't make any sense, Todd.
Hostetler's your father's friend.

01:24:59.209 --> 01:25:00.733
- Fuck my father!!

01:25:02.112 --> 01:25:04.012
I had the contract in my hand.

01:25:05.181 --> 01:25:08.275
And... Paul, he saw me waving

01:25:08.418 --> 01:25:09.817
and he smiled.

01:25:09.953 --> 01:25:11.443
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>

01:25:11.588 --> 01:25:15.922
Murdock, he must've followed me in his car.
And then he got out,

01:25:16.059 --> 01:25:18.994
he shot him, man!
He shot him in the fucking head!

01:25:19.129 --> 01:25:22.929
And then he showed up to work the next day
like nothing had happened.

01:25:23.066 --> 01:25:26.763
- Todd, it's alright. Look at me. Look at me.
Calm down, okay?

01:25:26.970 --> 01:25:29.029
Where's that contract?

01:25:40.216 --> 01:25:41.547
- Take it.

01:25:41.985 --> 01:25:43.782
I don't want it anymore.

01:25:50.627 --> 01:25:53.289
- Are you sure you're ready
to do this to your father?

01:25:53.429 --> 01:25:55.329
- Yeah.
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

01:25:55.465 --> 01:25:56.989
<font color="#D900D9">(HORN HONKING)</font>
- Shit.

01:25:57.133 --> 01:25:58.725
Get upstairs. Go!

01:26:33.670 --> 01:26:35.865
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font> That was an accident.

01:26:36.005 --> 01:26:39.532
It's Taggart, alright? Just calm down.
- Motherfucking fuck! Fuck!

01:26:39.676 --> 01:26:42.144
<font color="#D900D9">(ROARING)</font>
- Ah!

01:26:49.152 --> 01:26:51.552
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED GROANING)</font>

01:26:51.688 --> 01:26:53.121
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTING)</font>

01:26:58.828 --> 01:27:00.295
<font color="#D900D9">(PANTING)</font>

01:27:20.884 --> 01:27:22.317
You okay?

01:27:23.319 --> 01:27:24.513
- Yeah.

01:27:25.889 --> 01:27:27.322
Are you okay?

01:27:28.725 --> 01:27:30.522
- Yeah, I'm alright.
<font color="#D900D9">(ENGINE STARTING)</font>

01:28:07.931 --> 01:28:10.764
You got those reporters' email addresses?
- Yep.

01:28:11.935 --> 01:28:13.732
Billy, you sure about this?

01:28:14.771 --> 01:28:17.968
- If you don't hear from me in two hours,
you send that email okay?

01:28:18.574 --> 01:28:19.563
- Okay.

01:28:22.946 --> 01:28:25.039
- Thanks for being there, Katy.

01:28:26.950 --> 01:28:28.144
- Every time.

01:28:42.598 --> 01:28:46.261
<font color="#808080">WOMAN:</font> <i>Good evening. May I help you?</i>
- Yeah, tell the mayor it's Billy Taggart.

01:28:46.402 --> 01:28:47.960
<i>- One moment, please.</i>

01:28:56.179 --> 01:28:57.976
<font color="#D900D9">(GATE OPENING)</font>

01:29:11.828 --> 01:29:13.193
Mr. Mayor.

01:29:14.430 --> 01:29:15.397
- Billy.

01:29:15.531 --> 01:29:17.055
What a nice surprise.

01:29:17.200 --> 01:29:18.827
Thank you, Valerie.

01:29:20.436 --> 01:29:22.802
VCR. I haven't used one in years.

01:29:24.340 --> 01:29:26.638
Take your coat?
- No, I'm good.

01:29:27.844 --> 01:29:30.779
- I have to say, Billy,
you're looking a little worse for wear.

01:29:31.447 --> 01:29:33.312
- I got into a bit of a thing.

01:29:34.017 --> 01:29:36.008
- Well, I'm glad you made it out.

01:29:37.453 --> 01:29:39.819
Drink?
- Yeah, make it a double.

01:29:40.456 --> 01:29:42.014
- Atta boy, Billy.

01:29:43.026 --> 01:29:44.220
Alright.

01:29:47.463 --> 01:29:48.657
So...

01:29:49.465 --> 01:29:51.456
...how did Fitzgerald say it?

01:29:52.468 --> 01:29:57.030
"To the orgiastic future that year by year
recedes before us."

01:29:57.673 --> 01:29:58.867
Cheers.

01:30:02.745 --> 01:30:05.737
I don't even know what that means.
- Me neither.

01:30:05.882 --> 01:30:08.874
<font color="#D900D9">(MAYOR CHUCKLING)</font>
- What can I do for you, Billy?

01:30:10.486 --> 01:30:12.477
- I wanna know why you hired me.

01:30:13.056 --> 01:30:15.490
- Stick with the adultery narrative.

01:30:15.892 --> 01:30:17.052
It's sexier.

01:30:17.193 --> 01:30:18.922
- Yeah, lies are always sexier.

01:30:19.062 --> 01:30:21.553
Unfortunately, I've had enough this week
to last me a lifetime,

01:30:21.697 --> 01:30:24.029
so why don't you just tell me
the fuckin' truth?

01:30:26.269 --> 01:30:27.930
- The truth is...

01:30:28.071 --> 01:30:29.868
I hired you...

01:30:30.506 --> 01:30:32.064
...to investigate my wife.

01:30:32.208 --> 01:30:33.971
- Investigate her for what?

01:30:34.110 --> 01:30:37.079
- For not minding her own business,
is for what.

01:30:37.280 --> 01:30:39.714
For having a big mouth, is for what.

01:30:40.516 --> 01:30:42.916
For asking too many questions, is for what.

01:30:43.052 --> 01:30:45.077
You better be careful
following her example, Billy.

01:30:45.221 --> 01:30:48.088
I might have to hire someone
to investigate you.

01:30:48.224 --> 01:30:50.454
- Who you gonna have do that?
Your boy Murdock?

01:30:50.593 --> 01:30:53.084
I don't think he's available for the job.

01:30:54.297 --> 01:30:57.698
- I hope he didn't suffer.
- No more than Andrews did.

01:30:58.534 --> 01:31:01.765
- Damn shame what happened to that man.
- So tell me this, then, Mayor.

01:31:01.904 --> 01:31:06.364
Did you really think I'd let you turn me
into an accessory to murder? For $50,000?

01:31:06.509 --> 01:31:08.602
What, d'you think
I wouldn't ask any questions?

01:31:08.744 --> 01:31:10.905
Or d'you think I wouldn't get any answers?

01:31:11.547 --> 01:31:14.015
- What answers you got, Billy?
- Oh, I know Andrews

01:31:14.150 --> 01:31:17.608
was about to link you to Bolton Village.
That's the reason you got rid of him.

01:31:17.753 --> 01:31:20.813
- No, sir. Not me.
- Not you.

01:31:20.957 --> 01:31:22.788
The man you hired. Murdock.

01:31:22.925 --> 01:31:25.120
- Try getting that testimony.

01:31:25.261 --> 01:31:27.593
- Yeah. You're good, Mayor.
I give you that.

01:31:27.730 --> 01:31:29.823
You got it all worked out, huh?

01:31:29.966 --> 01:31:32.161
The denial about Bolton Village.

01:31:32.301 --> 01:31:35.293
The discount to Solstein Donagan.
The new big contract

01:31:35.438 --> 01:31:39.101
to the Rochway Group.
Nobody can do a goddamn thing about it, huh?

01:31:39.242 --> 01:31:42.370
'Cause anybody that could is either dead
or you bought 'em.

01:31:42.512 --> 01:31:45.140
I'm fuckin' impressed, Mayor. You're good.

01:31:45.281 --> 01:31:48.148
- Perhaps that's why the people
keep electing me, Billy.

01:31:48.985 --> 01:31:51.545
Because I simply get the job done.

01:31:51.687 --> 01:31:54.520
- So all this, it was all for the city?

01:31:54.657 --> 01:31:56.989
- Everything I do is for this great city.

01:31:57.126 --> 01:32:00.027
- The city doesn't own 50%
of Rochway Group, Mayor.

01:32:00.163 --> 01:32:01.630
You do.

01:32:02.365 --> 01:32:04.299
Look what I got.

01:32:09.372 --> 01:32:11.499
- What you got in your hand?

01:32:11.641 --> 01:32:13.268
- It's your fuckin' jugular, Mayor.

01:32:16.145 --> 01:32:19.171
Fifty percent of $4 billion
is a lot of fucking money.

01:32:20.383 --> 01:32:22.943
So here's how this works.
I got an email in my outbox

01:32:23.085 --> 01:32:25.519
with a scanned copy
of that Rochway contract attached to it.

01:32:25.655 --> 01:32:27.680
I click one button
and 100 different newsmen

01:32:27.823 --> 01:32:29.916
are gonna read your name
alongside Sam Lancaster's

01:32:30.059 --> 01:32:31.492
in black and white.

01:32:31.627 --> 01:32:34.118
Don't worry Mayor,
I got the original nice and safe.

01:32:34.263 --> 01:32:36.754
You resign, you step down,
I'll keep my mouth shut.

01:32:36.899 --> 01:32:39.026
Those emails'll never see the light of day.

01:32:39.168 --> 01:32:41.193
But that Bolton Village deal... is dead.

01:32:41.337 --> 01:32:45.433
Now you wanna tear down
100 other projects as a civilian, so be it.

01:32:45.575 --> 01:32:48.908
But Bolton Village is gonna stand
and you're gonna walk away.

01:32:49.045 --> 01:32:51.411
That's the deal, Mayor.
I suggest you take it.

01:32:51.547 --> 01:32:52.639
- Counteroffer.
- No need.

01:32:52.782 --> 01:32:55.774
I got nothing left for you to threaten.

01:32:55.918 --> 01:32:58.910
- I want the originals,
I want all the copies,

01:32:59.055 --> 01:33:01.080
and I want your case file.

01:33:01.224 --> 01:33:03.215
By... 9 a.m. tomorrow.

01:33:03.359 --> 01:33:04.849
- You're done, motherfucker.

01:33:05.428 --> 01:33:09.194
You are done.
- You ever spend a goddamned minute

01:33:09.332 --> 01:33:11.892
thinking why I chose you, Taggart?

01:33:12.034 --> 01:33:14.059
And I did choose you.

01:33:14.870 --> 01:33:16.667
I chose you.

01:33:18.074 --> 01:33:19.837
Because I own you.

01:33:20.876 --> 01:33:24.243
Now, you'll gonna have to excuse
the quality of the videotape.

01:33:25.248 --> 01:33:28.740
It was shot on one of those camcorders
they used to sell you hot,

01:33:28.884 --> 01:33:30.442
40 bucks on 8th Avenue.

01:33:31.887 --> 01:33:34.355
But I think you're about to see
the big picture.

01:33:35.725 --> 01:33:36.987
<i>- Hey, yo!</i>

01:33:37.126 --> 01:33:39.253
<i>First off, let me say welcome.</i>

01:33:39.395 --> 01:33:42.091
<i>Welcome to Bolton Village.</i>
- What the fuck is this?

01:33:42.231 --> 01:33:43.425
<i>- Ah, what's your name, fool?</i>

01:33:43.566 --> 01:33:46.831
<i>- They call me Alex, but you can call me...</i>
- What the fuck is this?!

01:33:46.969 --> 01:33:48.960
<i>- ... EI Guapo!
- EI Stupid.</i>

01:33:49.105 --> 01:33:52.597
<i>Yo, we just coolin' out,
me and my man David on the camcorder.</i>

01:33:52.742 --> 01:33:54.141
<i>- Hell, yes, the boy David.</i>

01:33:54.277 --> 01:33:56.142
<i>Hello.</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)</font>

01:33:56.279 --> 01:33:58.941
<i>- No, no, wait. I got a pocketful of cash,</i>

01:33:59.081 --> 01:34:03.848
<i>and we looking to have some fun tonight.
So we gonna hit up the usual spots,</i>

01:34:03.986 --> 01:34:06.045
<i>maybe get into something unusual.
- Hell yeah.</i>

01:34:06.188 --> 01:34:08.952
<font color="#808080">TAGGART:</font> <i>Drop the gun, Mikey!
Drop the fucking gun!</i>

01:34:08.991 --> 01:34:11.960
<font color="#808080">ALEX:</font> <i>What the fuck?!
- Drop the fucking gun!</i>

01:34:12.094 --> 01:34:14.775
<font color="#808080">MIKEY:</font> <i>Yo, chill, man! What the fuck?
- Mikey, we just wanna talk.</i>

01:34:19.769 --> 01:34:21.464
<font color="#D900D9">(PANTING)</font>

01:34:21.604 --> 01:34:23.299
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font>

01:34:25.141 --> 01:34:27.905
<i>Drop the fucking gun.
- Man, what the fuck, man?</i>

01:34:28.044 --> 01:34:30.239
<i>- It's okay, Mikey. We just wanna talk.</i>

01:34:34.517 --> 01:34:37.247
<i>- Oh, shit, man!
C'mon, get the fuck outta here!</i>

01:34:43.759 --> 01:34:46.091
<font color="#D900D9">(SIRENS WAILING)</font>

01:34:51.467 --> 01:34:54.163
<i>Oh, shit, man!
C'mon, get the fuck out of here!</i>

01:34:58.774 --> 01:35:00.935
- How's your memory now, Billy?

01:35:05.181 --> 01:35:07.775
Now, there's something
that your average citizen...

01:35:10.386 --> 01:35:12.183
...just wouldn't understand.

01:35:13.356 --> 01:35:14.789
But I do.

01:35:16.359 --> 01:35:18.190
You see, we...

01:35:18.327 --> 01:35:20.454
we take because we can.

01:35:21.364 --> 01:35:22.797
We take...

01:35:24.200 --> 01:35:25.792
...because it feels good.

01:35:27.336 --> 01:35:29.804
The only difference between you and I...

01:35:30.573 --> 01:35:33.098
...is that you've gone and done it
on videotape.

01:35:33.242 --> 01:35:35.540
Like I was saying, I want the original,

01:35:35.678 --> 01:35:39.205
all the copies and the case file,
by the morning.

01:35:39.815 --> 01:35:41.373
You can have this copy.

01:35:41.817 --> 01:35:45.378
I transferred it to disk... seven years ago.

01:35:56.031 --> 01:35:57.225
- Nat?

01:37:09.472 --> 01:37:12.669
<i>- We take... because it feels good.</i>

