<i>The only difference between you and I</i>

01:37:16.445 --> 01:37:19.312
<i>is that you've gone and done it on videotape.</i>

01:37:20.449 --> 01:37:23.009
<i>Like I was saying, I want the original,</i>

01:37:23.152 --> 01:37:26.417
<i>all the copies and the case file,
